| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7033 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 71fe3542-495f-5489-abcb-f6af7bc91ab7"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
